data.description: A beautiful well maintained 3 bedroom plus den, 2 bath and oversized 2 car garage, centrally located within in highly sought after gated-community-Stoneybrook in Estero! Excellent amenities including golf course (pay as you play), community pool (3 pools), clubhouse, tennis courts, playground, bocce ball, pickleball,and more! Upgrades to include newer roof (2018), newer hot water heater, A/C 2022! Plantation shutters in every room, hardwood floors in living/dining area and bamboo wood in all bedrooms, surround sound speakers. Kitchen updated with Quartzite countertops and Island, newer refrigerator, dishwasher, and disposal. Recently painted interior and exterior of home. Security system wired in home, buyer may activate if chooses to. Large screened lanai for outdoor entertaining and room for a pool or garden. Stoneybrook offers something for everyone and especially for the golf enthusiast (course on-site)! Close to Coconut Pointe Mall, Miramar outlets, Gulf Coast town center, FGCU, and the beautiful gulf coast beaches! Come see for yourself today!!
